<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="ko">
<head>
<meta charset="utf-8">
<title>Node.js 게시판</title>
<link rel="stylesheet" href="https://maxcdn.bootstrapcdn.com/bootstrap/3.3.2/css/bootstrap.min.css">
</head>
<body>
	<header>
		<div class="container">
			<h1><%=title%></h1>
		</div>
	</header>
	<div class="container">
		<section>
			<form class="form-horizontal" method="post" action="/board/<%=article._id%>?_method=delete">
				<div class="form-group">
					<label for="writer" class="col-sm-1 control-label">작성자</label>
					<div class="col-sm-3">
						<input type="text" class="form-control" readonly value="<%=article.writer%>">
					</div>
				</div>
				<div class="form-group">
					<label for="title" class="col-sm-1 control-label">제목</label>
					<div class="col-sm-11">
						<input type="text" class="form-control" readonly value="<%=article.title%>">
					</div>
				</div>
				<div class="form-group">
					<label for="content" class="sr-only">내용</label>
					<div class="col-sm-12">
						<textarea rows="15" class="form-control" readonly><%=article.content%></textarea>
					</div>
				</div>
				<hr>
				<div class="form-group">
					<div class="text-center">
						<a href="/board/" class="btn btn-primary">목록</a>
						<button type="submit" class="btn btn-default">삭제</button>
					</div>
				</div>
			</form>
		</section>
	</div>
	<footer>
		<div class="container">
			<p class="text-muted">게시판 정책 및 약관 회사소개 광고 마이비즈니스제휴 제안 이용약관 개인정보취급방침 청소년보호 정책 고객센터</p>
		</div>
	</footer>
</body>
</html>